{"id": "1284908851065262163", "channel_id": "1284908851065262163", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "在點擊喚醒體詳情的時候\n由於詳情跟靈知深化的按鈕都在同個位置\n很容易一個卡頓連續點擊兩三次\n啪一下等級上限道具就沒了\n也沒個額外的確定按鈕\n\n另外深潛兌換的三隻角色聽說是不能回朔的\n如果誤用等級上限提升道具更心疼\n\n附上影片\n艾瑞卡噴到62級強迫症玩家痛苦的要命", "timestamp": "2024-09-15T16:09:02.546000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "➕", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "1️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1284908851451265044", "filename": "2024-09-16-00-07-34.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 598804, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1284908851065262163/1284908851451265044/2024-09-16-00-07-34.mp4?ex=69cbf19e&is=69caa01e&hm=359beb2a88f53a83aa8417007db9f8477854b7063f86c178b1aacc8e19f56387&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1284908851065262163", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "靈知深化很容易誤觸", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
